The paper also discusses how the modification works as a regularization, which is a topic in the sub-category of "cs.AI" (Artificial Intelligence). Furthermore, the paper mentions that the method can be applied to regression tasks in computer vision, which is a topic in the sub-category of "cs.CV" (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition).
